node.title: ACT records one case of Omicron COVID-19 variant
node.alt: A vial labeled 'Vaccine COVID-19 Omicron variant' and test sample tubes are pictured in this illustration photo.
node.description: ACT Health confirmsÂ an Omicron COVID-19 infection in the territory, in an individual who has not travelled overseas.
node.content: ["ACT Health has confirmed an Omicron COVID-19 infection in the territory, in an individual who has not travelled overseas.", "The person is fully vaccinated and returned a positive COVID-19 test on Wednesday December 1.", "Following genome sequencing, the case was today confirmed as the Omicron variant.", "It is not yet known if the\u00a0case was acquired in the ACT or NSW.", "More to come."]
